{"tid":1742470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［理性討論］我地係咪應該係今個星期六日暫停一下嗰黎明行動？","createTime":"2019-11-20T21:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T21:45:48.000Z","uid":231478,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eb701170131753faabef3fdfe2b30b742a2fc95a","tid":1742470,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:26:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">注意 係暫停 同埋係今個禮拜 唔好屌我先</span></span><br />\n唔係話聽朝停 係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今個禮拜六日</span></span>停<br />\n我明黎明行動 對政府打擊真係好大 嗰股市係咁跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲搞到好多手足俾狗咬/俾藍絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n敵人反對的，姐係我地方向正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我唔想俾特首有任何藉口推遲嗰選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/直接建制當選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以係今個星期六日停一停 下個禮拜再繼續翻 唔好俾政府賴落我地度<br />\n：無得投票？ 要怪就怪班「暴徒」lol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係到而家都覺得選舉係有用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到而家都覺得選舉可以踢走建制架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我貼條link啦 我個人覺得佢分析得幾有道理 港共政府其實一直想分化我地 乜9責任都推曬落我地到<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GPpC8vKjPJs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGPpC8vKjPJs&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzi2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=2a8a5b23\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GPpC8vKjPJs</a><br />\n <br />\n重點：13:42<br />\n對家搵人製造暴力屈我地嘅應對方法：13:53<br />\n<br />\n我星期日朝早7:30要起身投票啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講明先：依場運動到而家都未輸係因為無大台 我只係發表下個人意見 如果覺得唔work嘅 可以唔洗聽我講 我開po純粹係想俾大家理性討論下我地應該點應對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d6ee3c02d1614cfae838037bbee6c32d892a82","tid":1742470,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:28:19.000Z","msg":"有無巴打/絲打一齊討論下？"},{"pid":"ebc26348ba201dffcc918629dee7889e1c9273b9","tid":1742470,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:32:26.000Z","msg":"係咪太早 無人幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1f7e0c4ef723de1aeb193eb3f4062ec02af244","tid":1742470,"uid":119396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:38:44.000Z","msg":"不嬲都唔塞週末"},{"pid":"1ca327f4662d1923b747d45730913f3be3bff12c","tid":1742470,"uid":142522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:45:48.000Z","msg":"好似星期六日本來都冇搞"}]}